test: add comprehensive test suite (772 new tests, 1982 total)

14-workstream parallel test build covering all layers:
- Integration: multi-household workflows, snowball lifecycle, baby steps
- Security: IDOR, role escalation, merge RPC auth, migration 016 regressions
- API: merge RPC contracts, notify-event handler, extract-slip edge paths
- Financial: budget invariants, snowball projections, property-based (fast-check)
- UI/UX: WCAG 2.2 accessibility, household switching, budget flows
- Sync integrity: concurrent users, DLQ, soft-delete gaps, restore ordering
- Boot recovery: BootErrorBoundary, BootRecoveryGate, error states
- Offline-first: airplane mode, queue buildup, batch limits
- Domain gaps: households, scoring, coaching, forecasting, baby step helpers
- Screens: 4 zero-coverage screens + expanded existing screen tests
- Hooks/stores/components: 7 hooks, 9 stores, 20+ components, nav guards
- Data/infra: migration runner, crash monitoring, SlipQueueRepo, sync errors
- Factory: shared test factories + 200-transaction scenario seed data
- Currency formatting, navigation flows, first-time user empty states

Documents 18 known architectural gaps with TODO markers.
